# Student

Student Information is a REST API to allow users to view and update student information. 

# Allowed HTTP requests: 
<pre>
PUT     : Update resource
POST    : Create resource
GET     : Get a resource or list of resources 
DELETE  : To delete a resource
</pre>

# Group Student

**User attributes:**
- id `(HexString)`    : Unique Identifier
- name `(String)`     : Name of the student
- roll `(String)`     : Roll of the student 

## Student Collection [/student]

### List All Students [GET /student/]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

