### Create a New Student [POST /student/]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "name" : "John Doe",
            "roll" : "65"
        }
        
+ Response 201 (application/json)
        
        {
            "_id"  : "fd16c23609200c15a47c8",
            "name" : "John Doe",
            "roll" : "65"
        }
        
### List Student by id [GET /student/{id}]
Retrieve a single Student by id
+ Parameters
    + id (required, HexString, `5cbd75018f85d11a6c9a71c3` ... HexString `id`  of the student to perform action with)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "_id" :"5cbd75018f85d11a6c9a71c3",
            "name":"abc",
            "roll":"514"
        }
        
### Update an Student by ID [PUT /student/{id}]      
Update an student under the collection with given id
+ Parameters
    + id (required, HexString, `5cbd75018f85d11a6c9a71c3` ... HexString `id`  of the student to perform action with)

+ Request (application/json) 

        {
            "name": "Jane Doe",
            "roll": "514"
        }
        
+ Response 201 (application/json)

        {
            "_id" :"5cbd75018f85d11a6c9a71c3",
            "name":"Jane Doe",
            "roll":"514"
        }
        
### Remove a Student [DELETE /{id}]
+ Parameters
    + id (required, HexString, `5cbd75018f85d11a6c9a71c3` ... HexString `id`  of the student to perform action with)
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "_id" :"5cbd75018f85d11a6c9a71c3",
            "name":"abc",
            "roll":"514"
        }